## 5. Base Classes

### 5.1 SectionCard

**Card:** `SectionCard extends CardDef`

**Purpose:** Base class that all section cards extend. Provides common fields and ensures consistent behavior.

**Location:** `sections/section-card.gts`

**Fields:**
- `sectionId: StringField` â€” Anchor ID (e.g., "001-hero")
- `sectionNumber: StringField` â€” Display number (e.g., "001")
- `sectionLabel: StringField` â€” Display label (e.g., "Overview")
- `showInNav: BooleanField` â€” Should appear in nav dropdown? (default: true)

**Template:**
```gts
import { CardDef, Component, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import StringField from 'https://cardstack.com/base/string';
import BooleanField from 'https://cardstack.com/base/boolean';

export class SectionCard extends CardDef {
  static displayName = 'Section';

  @field sectionId = contains(StringField);
  @field sectionNumber = contains(StringField);
  @field sectionLabel = contains(StringField);
  @field showInNav = contains(BooleanField, {
    computeVia: function() { return true; }
  });

  // Subclasses override with their own isolated template
  static isolated = class Isolated extends Component<typeof this> {
    <template>
      <section id={{@model.sectionId}} class="section">
        <div class="section-content">
          <!-- Override in subclass -->
        </div>
      </section>
    </template>
  };
}
```

---

### 5.2 PageSectionField (FieldDef)

**Field:** `PageSectionField extends FieldDef`

**Purpose:** Wraps a section card with metadata for the layout orchestrator. Used in `containsMany(PageSectionField)` on layout cards.

**Location:** `fields/page-section-field.gts`

**Fields:**
- `sectionId: StringField` â€” Anchor ID for scrolling (e.g., "001-hero")
- `sectionNumber: StringField` â€” Displayed in nav dropdown (e.g., "001")
- `sectionLabel: StringField` â€” Displayed in nav dropdown (e.g., "Overview")
- `showInNav: BooleanField` â€” Should this section appear in nav dropdown?
- `content: linksTo(SectionCard)` â€” The actual section card (polymorphic)

**Template:**
```gts
import { FieldDef, Component, field, contains, linksTo } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import StringField from 'https://cardstack.com/base/string';
import BooleanField from 'https://cardstack.com/base/boolean';
import { SectionCard } from '../sections/section-card';

export class PageSectionField extends FieldDef {
  static displayName = 'Page Section';

  @field sectionId = contains(StringField);
  @field sectionNumber = contains(StringField);
  @field sectionLabel = contains(StringField);
  @field showInNav = contains(BooleanField, {
    computeVia: function() { return true; }
  });
  @field content = linksTo(SectionCard);

  static embedded = class Embedded extends Component<typeof this> {
    <template>
      <div class="page-section-wrapper" id={{@model.sectionId}}>
        <@fields.content @format="isolated" />
      </div>
    </template>
  };
}
```

**Usage in Layout:**
```gts
export class HomeLayoutCard extends CardDef {
  @field sections = containsMany(PageSectionField);

  static isolated = class Isolated extends Component<typeof this> {
    <template>
      <main class="sections-container">
        {{#each @fields.sections as |sectionField|}}
          <sectionField @format="embedded" />
        {{/each}}
      </main>
    </template>
  };
}
```

