- `headlineWord2: StringField` â€” "Everything."
- `tagline: StringField` â€” "Build what you use. Use what you build."
- `description: StringField` â€” Full paragraph
- `primaryCtaText: StringField` â€” "Start Building"
- `primaryCtaUrl: UrlField`
- `secondaryCtaText: StringField` â€” "Read the Vision â†’"
- `secondaryCtaUrl: UrlField`
- `badges: containsMany(BadgeField)` â€” Open source strip items
- `backgroundGrid: linksTo(() => AnimatedGrid)` â€” Animated card background

**BadgeField (FieldDef):**
- `icon: StringField` â€” GitHub icon SVG or emoji
- `label: StringField` â€” "100% Open Source"
- `url: UrlField` â€” Optional link

**Template Features:**
- Composited `AnimatedGrid` card as background layer
- Gradient text on highlight word
- Frosted glass effect on text container
- Open source badge strip

**Composition Pattern:**
The hero section uses the AnimatedGrid card as a background layer:

```gts
static isolated = class Isolated extends Component<typeof this> {
  <template>
    <section class="hero-section">
      {{! Background layer - composited card }}
      {{#if @model.backgroundGrid}}
        <div class="background-layer">
          <@fields.backgroundGrid @format="isolated" />
        </div>
      {{/if}}

      {{! Content layer }}
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-eyebrow">{{@model.eyebrow}}</div>
        <h1 class="hero-headline">
          <span class="word-1">{{@model.headlineWord1}}</span>
          <span class="word-2">{{@model.headlineWord2}}</span>
        </h1>
        <!-- Rest of hero content -->
      </div>
    </section>

    <style scoped>
      .hero-section {
        position: relative;
        padding-block: var(--hero-padding-block, var(--section-padding-block));
        padding-inline: var(--section-padding-inline);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .background-layer {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        z-index: 0;
        opacity: 0.6; /* Subtle background effect */
      }

      .hero-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        max-width: var(--section-max-width);
        margin-inline: auto;
      }
    </style>
  </template>
};
```

