### Advanced: Responsive Grid Columns API

You can also communicate layout parameters like grid columns:

```css
/* Orchestrator defines grid API */
.sections-container {
  --catalog-columns: 4;
  --catalog-gap: 1.5rem;
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .sections-container {
    --catalog-columns: 3;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .sections-container {
    --catalog-columns: 2;
  }
}
```

```css
/* Section consumes the grid API */
.catalog-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(var(--catalog-columns, 4), 1fr);
  gap: var(--catalog-gap, 1.5rem);
}
```

